snippet.title: Rust Trailer - 2018  (Remaster)
snippet.description:
Buy Rust: http://store.steampowered.com/app/252490/Rust/

♫ Song:
Grifta - Risico

This is a remastered version of the trailer by Surge. Why? Well the
game is out of early access now and the footage in the trailer for Rust in 2017 is outdated. It's actually the 4th generation of the trailer, if you take some research.
Surge: https://www.youtube.com/user/SurgedEdits

*ALSO*
If you want more content like this, be sure to subscribe to my channel.
Don't get turned off by the fact that I don't upload in English. If I get a lot of support from this video, I'll start to record in English!

And finally: I wouldn't be able to make this video without the help of:
-PenguinSi (server host, actor & co-editor).
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5orLxMSiFexRPDyA0Tf0KQ
-Aney            (actor)
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpKjojwuyzVF4AtF1O5QwFg
-V1dus         (actor)
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCAHIUfoyZgCjeawCFW2AVQ
-Vici              (actor)
-Fiery Toots (actor)
